{"tid":38834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"季候風來臨　明早多區13度及乾燥","createTime":"2016-12-14T07:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T07:37:50.000Z","uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee53e045e29802cdf0a7899f6d1763fd86ba2c64","tid":38834,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/xi.UiuPXA1EzA1zJuryq3A--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQwMDtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20161214a125552.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fxi.UiuPXA1EzA1zJuryq3A--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQwMDtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20161214a125552.jpg&d=z0qExKJve019zTluS%2Ft0swT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=437db8ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/xi.UiuPXA1EzA1zJuryq3A--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQwMDtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20161214a125552.jpg</a><br />\n【星島日報報道】東北季候風來臨，天氣開始轉涼，今日氣溫明顯下跌，昨日最高約26度，但今日中午普遍只有22度左右，最高23度，入夜後氣溫會進一步下跌。根據天文台自動分區天氣預報，今晚6時將會降至21度，晚上10時左右只有17度。<br />\n　　天文台表示，一股強烈的東北季候風會在未來一兩天持續影響廣東沿岸，該區氣溫將逐步下降，天氣乾燥，隨著季候風於下週初逐漸緩和，華南氣溫將會回升。<br />\n　　周四清早氣溫進一步下降，大埔、上水、青衣及將軍澳於明早7時，預料只有13度，沙田、西貢及屯門亦只有14度，市區15度。濕度方面較為乾燥，明日中午大埔及將軍澳等或只有54%至55%。"},{"pid":"6b53a1f66c9c6554dfb39121d25fd0b500f1e260","tid":38834,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於可以著黑絲保暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}